rating_comment: At first I would like to thank you Rahi bhai. It was my first stay with my whole family. The way he communicates, the way he deals its amazing. The place is very net and clean. I love to stay there again…. Mr. Rahi help me a lot. Awesome host and I must say building staff Anwar was great too. I am glad I chose Rahi’s place to stay.

This place is very familiar friendly and close to all amenities.

Planning to stay again here next year or end of this year for 4-5 weeks.
We are very thankful to the caretaker of this place who helped us lots time to time.
